TitleEnglish: Inazuma Eleven GO the Movie: The Ultimate Bonds Gryphon
SummaryEnglish: The Kaminarimon Soccer Club, led by Tenma Matsukaze, continues to fight against the Fifth Sector, a soccer management organization that manages even victory and defeat. Meanwhile, the Fifth Sector ordered us to participate in the training camp. Tenma and his friends head to God Eden, an island with a vast nature area with a training camp.
